---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact Savelle Design - Let's Discuss Your Project"
  description="Get in touch to discuss your web design, landing page, brand identity, or email campaign project. Based in Scottsdale, AZ, available for remote work worldwide. Response within 24 hours."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6">Let's Work Together</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-600 max-w-3xl">
        I'm always open to discussing new projects and opportunities. Whether you need a landing page, a website refresh, or help with your brand, I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Full-width border -->
  <div class="border-t border-zinc-200"></div>

  <!-- Email CTA -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6">
          Get in Touch
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-600 mb-8">
          The best way to reach me is by email. I typically respond within 24 hours and look forward to learning about your project.
        </p>
        <a
          href="mailto:savellem@gmail.com"
          class="inline-block px-12 py-4 bg-zinc-900 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-colors font-medium text-lg mb-4"
        >
          savellem@gmail.com
        </a>
        <p class="text-zinc-600">
          Or call me at <a href="tel:+16029311474" class="text-zinc-900 font-medium hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors">602-931-1474</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Information -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-zinc-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-900 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Location</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600">
                Based in Scottsdale, Arizona<br />
                Available for remote work worldwide
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-900 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Response Time</h3>
              <p class="text-zinc-600">
                Usually within 24 hours on weekdays
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-zinc-900 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-2">Connect</h3>
              <a
                href="https://linkedin.com"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-zinc-600 hover:text-zinc-900 transition-colors"
              >
                Find me on LinkedIn
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Full-width border -->
  <div class="border-t border-zinc-200"></div>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">What's your typical project timeline?</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600">
            Project timelines vary depending on scope and complexity. A typical website project takes 4-8 weeks
            from initial consultation to launch. I'll provide a detailed timeline during our initial discussion.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Do you work with clients remotely?</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600">
            Yes! I work with clients worldwide and have established processes for remote collaboration,
            including regular video calls, project management tools, and clear communication.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">What information do you need to get started?</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600">
            To begin, I'll need an overview of your project goals, target audience, timeline, and budget.
            Any existing brand materials, content, or examples of designs you like are also helpful.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 mb-3">Do you offer ongoing support?</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600">
            Yes, I offer maintenance and support packages for websites and ongoing design services
            for clients who need regular design work. We can discuss options that fit your needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
